nodes.text: Mos Anek was an outpost of the Sith Empire in the Jundland Wastes on the planet Tatooine during the Cold War.

Mos Anek was created for Star Wars: The Old Republic, a massively multiplayer online role-playing game released by BioWare on December 20, 2011. It appears as one of the Imperial settlements on the planet Tatooine.
